text: Qeysar (, meaning "Caesar") is a 1969 Iranian crime drama movie directed by Masoud Kimiai and starring Behrouz Vossoughi, Pouri Banai, Nasser Malekmotei, Jamshid Mashayekhi, Bahman Mofid. ==Other websites== * Category:1969 crime movies Category:1969 drama movies Category:1960s crime drama movies Category:Iranian movies Category:Movies directed by Masoud Kimiai
